=== Compliling ===

By now, you need to fill the ./deps by hands. Resulting deps should be like this:

$ ls -l ./deps
/couchbeam			(git://github.com/benoitc/couchbeam.git)
/rabbitmq-erlang-client		(hg clone http://hg.rabbitmq.com/rabbitmq-erlang-client/)
/rabbit_common			symlink to ./rabbitmq-erlang-client/dist/rabbit_common-0.0.0
/webmachine			(git://github.com/basho/webmachine.git)
/riak-erlang-client		(git://github.com/basho/riak-erlang-client.git)
/ibrowse			(git://github.com/cmullaparthi/ibrowse.git)

See https://github.com/matteoredaelli/ebot/wiki/Installation for more info about compiling.


